Fill 3-quart saucepan 2/3 full of water. Heat to boiling. Add contents of Pasta-Vegetable pouch to boiling water. Gently boil about 12 minutes or until pasta is tender; drain. Rinse with cold water until chilled; drain. Stir together Seasoning mix, oil, water and mustard in large bowl. Stir in pasta and Parmesan Topping. Stir cheese and ham into finished salad. Cover and refrigerate any remaining salad.